Goes the Neighborhood,"

00:36:43.200 --> 00:36:45.162
the WNYC podcast
about gentrification

00:36:45.162 --> 00:36:45.870
in New York City.

00:36:45.870 --> 00:36:46.840
PJ VOGT: It's really good.

