00:38:14.576 --> 00:38:16.200
I'm trying to think
of some other ones.

00:38:16.200 --> 00:38:18.345
They called a bunch of
places for a while asking

00:38:18.345 --> 00:38:20.970
if Tony Rice was there, and when
they'd say no, they'd be like,

00:38:20.970 --> 00:38:22.774
you just got pranked!

00:38:22.774 --> 00:38:23.690
PJ VOGT: That's funny.

00:38:23.690 --> 00:38:26.770
ALEX GOLDMAN:
Yeah, really funny.

00:38:26.770 --> 00:38:28.020
Definitely not for all tastes.

00:38:28.020 --> 00:38:29.040
Definitely not good.

00:38:32.100 --> 00:38:33.044
But I like it.

00:38:33.044 --> 00:38:33.960
SPEAKER 1: That works.

00:38:33.960 --> 00:38:34.290
All right.

